1. You have a total of 5 ships to complete your journey.  
2.There will be 3 hints hidden in your current location to help you get one step closer to the treasure.
3. The answer to the hint will be next location in the pirates journey. Each location brings you closer to the treasure. 
4. If you miss a hint you will lose a ship and will have to search for another hidden hint.
5. If you miss all three hints you will be promoted to next location with a loss of one life.
6. You need to reach the treasure in the least time.
So get Started and Enjoy!! 